  4. Reminder 流程(独立 cron,不打断主线)

  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
  │  Invoke-WeComAuditOpsReminder.ps1                                 │
  │   参数: -Phase Analysis|Validate -Environment -Sequence -Severity│
  │         -StartDate(backfill) -FailOnSendError                    │
  └─────────┬────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
            │
            ▼
    Resolve-ScheduleCycle
            │
            ▼
    Cycle-day guard:
      非 backfill 且 cycle.EndDate ≠ today
         │
         └─YES─► Write-Warning + exit 0  (避免错日子打扰)
         NO
         │
         ▼
    New-AuditTokenMap  → resolvedSourceFolder
            │
            ▼
    Test-PreflightReady
     (Analysis→SourceFolder / Validate→ValidationFolder)
            │
     ┌──────┴──────┐
     ▼             ▼
    AllReady=true  缺文件
     │             │
     ▼             ▼
    log SKIPPED   Resolve-NotificationConfig
    exit 0         │
                   ▼
                cert? ──NO──► log SKIPPED + exit 0
                   │
                  YES
                   ▼
                Send-AuditReminderNotification
                  ├─ To: OpsTeam (无 CC)
                  ├─ Subject: [WeCom Audit][ENV] <Severity> (Seq) - Pre-<Phase>
                  ├─ Body: missing files + deadline (NextSchedulerTime)
                  └─ catch: log FAILED
                            if -FailOnSendError: exit 1
                            else: exit 0
            │
            ▼
    写 reminders/reminder-yyyyMMdd-Phase-HHmm.log
    exit 0(cron 路径永远不报红)

